  "title": "🎲 Casino Dealer – Up to $2,800 Monthly + Extensive Benefits| No Experience Needed!",
  "description": "<p>💰 Salary</p><p>Up to $2.8k Basic + Allowances + Bonuses</p><p>🕒 Working Hours / Shifts</p><ul><li>8hr Rotational shifts (morning, afternoon, evening, overnight)</li><li>Transport provided for shifts that end after midnight</li></ul><p>📍 Work Location</p><p>Nearest MRT: Bayfront</p><p>🎯 Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Operate gaming tables and ensure smooth gameplay</li><li>Deliver excellent customer service on the gaming floor</li><li>Handle chips, table arrangements, and guest interactions</li><li>Follow SOPs and uphold safety & regulatory standards</li><li>Support operations to maintain a high-quality guest experience</li></ul><p>📝 Job Requirements</p><ul><li>No experience required – full training provided</li><li>Comfortable with rotational and overnight shifts</li><li>Positive attitude, willing to learn, professional under pressure</li></ul><p>🎉 Employee Benefits</p><ul><li>Duty meals provided</li><li>Uniforms + laundry service</li></ul><p></p><p>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: admin@crew.sg</p><p>For a quicker reply, text us at: +65 91728913</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period, and expected salary.</p><p>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Branson Yong</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>EA 24C2435</p>",
